OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1781621296
OL,3,CFormer Labour deputy leader Roy
OL,4,CHattersley dies, aged 93
OL,6,FRoy Hattersley, the former Labour
OL,7,Fdeputy leader, has died aged 93, with
OL,8,FSir Keir Starmer leading tributes to
OL,9,Fhis "decades of service".
OL,11,FBorn in Sheffield, Mr Hattersley went
OL,12,Fon to study Economics at the
OL,13,FUniversity of Hull. From there, he
OL,14,Fbriefly worked at a Sheffield
OL,15,Fsteelworks before pursuing a career in
OL,16,Fpolitics.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
