CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1781621296
OL,3,CFormer Labour deputy leader Roy
OL,4,CHattersley dies, aged 93
OL,6,FLabour deputy leader Lucy Powell
OL,7,Fposted: "This is sad news. Roy
OL,8,FHattersley, best known for being Neil
OL,9,FKinnock's deputy leader, shaped the
OL,10,FLabour Party and British politics.
OL,12,F"He was a giant of our movement and of
OL,13,Fthat generation of politicians.
OL,15,F"I met him a few times and he was
OL,16,Falways kind, thoughtful and full of
OL,17,Fsound advice."
OL,26,@oD@IOUtD@AOUwD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
