PN,33707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F337A1781621296
OL,3,CFormer Labour deputy leader Roy
OL,4,CHattersley dies, aged 93
OL,6,FLabour MP Dame Emily Thornberry told
OL,7,FBBC Radio 4's The Westminster Hour: "I
OL,8,Fremember he was a passionate European.
OL,9,FHe was seen as being on the right and
OL,10,Fthen he fell out with the Blairite and
OL,11,Fwas passionate critic of Blair as well.
OL,13,F"Whatever he believed he believed a
OL,14,F100% and he expressed it with great
OL,15,Fclarity and we need more politicians
OL,16,Flike him."
OL,26,@oD@eOUuD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
